r mt-3\">\n            <p class=\"text-[13px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-bold bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-inner border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-slate-700/50\">قم بنسخ البيانات المطلوبة من الصندوق أعلاه ☝️</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"my-12\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-8\">\n        <div class=\"p-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10 text-white shrink-0\">\n            <svg class=\"w-7 h-7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"font-black text-3xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight drop-shadow-sm\">آلية التثبيت والتشغيل خطوة بخطوة</h3>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-l from-amber-50 to-orange-50/30 dark:from-amber-900/20 dark:to-orange-900/10 border border-amber-200/60 dark:border-amber-700/30 p-5 rounded-2xl mb-8 flex items-start sm:items-center gap-4 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden\">\n        <div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-400 to-orange-500\"></div>\n        <div class=\"p-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-amber-100 dark:border-slate-700 text-amber-500 shrink-0\">\n            <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"></path></svg>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-200 font-extrabold text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed pt-1 sm:pt-0\">يرجى إدخال بيانات تسجيل الدخول (اسم المستخدم وكلمة المرور) بدقة تامة وبدون أي مسافات إضافية لتجنب أخطاء المصادقة عند تسجيل الدخول.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mt-6\">\n        <div class=\"flex gap-4 sm:gap-6 relative\">\n            <div class=\"absolute right-6 sm:right-7 top-14 bottom-[-1rem] w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 opacity-20 rounded-full z-0\"></div>\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 p-0.5 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10\">\n                <div class=\"w-full h-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl sm:text-2xl text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">1</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex-1 pb-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800/50 p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-[1.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\">\n                    <p class=\"text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.8] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-bold tracking-wide\"><strong>لأجهزة الهواتف (Android):</strong> قم بتنزيل التطبيق وتثبيته مباشرة وبشكل آمن من متجر Google Play عبر الرابط المرفق أسفل المقال.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex gap-4 sm:gap-6 relative\">\n            <div class=\"absolute right-6 sm:right-7 top-14 bottom-[-1rem] w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 opacity-20 rounded-full z-0\"></div>\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 p-0.5 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10\">\n                <div class=\"w-full h-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl sm:text-2xl text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">2</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex-1 pb-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800/50 p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-[1.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\">\n                    <p class=\"text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.8] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-bold tracking-wide\"><strong>للشاشات الذكية وأجهزة TV Box:</strong> ستحتاج إلى تطبيق \"Downloader\". قم بتثبيته أولاً من متجر التطبيقات الخاص بشاشتك (متوفر زر للتحميل بالأسفل).</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex gap-4 sm:gap-6 relative\">\n            <div class=\"absolute right-6 sm:right-7 top-14 bottom-[-1rem] w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 opacity-20 rounded-full z-0\"></div>\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 p-0.5 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10\">\n                <div class=\"w-full h-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl sm:text-2xl text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">3</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex-1 pb-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800/50 p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-[1.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\">\n                    <p class=\"text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.8] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-bold tracking-wide\">افتح تطبيق Downloader في شاشتك، وتوجه إلى خانة البحث أو إدخال الروابط (URL)، واكتب الكود المباشر التالي: <strong class=\"text-blue-600 dir-ltr inline-block bg-white px-2 rounded\">4141801</strong> ثم اضغط على Go للبدء بالتحميل التلقائي.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex gap-4 sm:gap-6 relative\">\n            <div class=\"absolute right-6 sm:right-7 top-14 bottom-[-1rem] w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 opacity-20 rounded-full z-0\"></div>\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 p-0.5 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10\">\n                <div class=\"w-full h-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl sm:text-2xl text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">4</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex-1 pb-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800/50 p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-[1.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\">\n                    <p class=\"text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.8] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-bold tracking-wide\">بعد اكتمال التثبيت بنجاح (سواء على الهاتف أو الشاشة الذكية)، قم بفتح تطبيق Lion TV.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex gap-4 sm:gap-6 relative\">\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 p-0.5 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10\">\n                <div class=\"w-full h-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl sm:text-2xl text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">5</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex-1 pb-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800/50 p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-[1.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\">\n                    <p class=\"text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.8] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-bold tracking-wide\">انسخ بيانات الحساب (Username / Password) من صندوق الأكواد المرفق أعلاه، وألصقها في الحقول المخصصة، ثم اضغط على تسجيل الدخول (Login) للاستمتاع بالمحتوى المجاني.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <sec